  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As you prepare a trap to be sprung, you infuse its mechanism with chakra to increase its effectiveness. This jutsu's casting time equals how long it takes to prepare the trap being used as a component. The chakra poured into the trap lasts for 24 hours. When the trap is activated during the duration of this jutsu, it gains an additional effect: the trap deals damage equal to double your unarmed attack, and its DC gains a bonus equal to your Strength Modifier. If the trap was a restraining trap, the target must make a Constitution save or gain a rank of Slowed. If the trap was a weapon trap, its damage is chakra-enhanced and also deals chakra damage equal to half the trap's total damage</p>",
